---
title: Hoisin Chicken Gyozas and Five Spice Fries with Sambal Pear Slaw
description: Pronounced gee-oh-zuh, our Hoisin Chicken Gyozas and Five Spice Fries take inspiration from Chinese flavours. Hoisin contains Chinese Five Spice, rice vinegar and red miso which gives it its delicious sweet-umami flavour.
